ream.\", \"from\": 3834, \"to\": 3955, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best riders\", \"from\": 3860, \"to\": 3875}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 3879, \"to\": 3888}, {\"ngram\": \"a big team\", \"from\": 3907, \"to\": 3917}, {\"ngram\": \"my dream\", \"from\": 3946, \"to\": 3954}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am very happy to see Eyeru [Tesfoam Gebru] in the Olympics.\", \"from\": 3957, \"to\": 4019, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Eyeru\", \"from\": 3981, \"to\": 3986}, {\"ngram\": \"[Tesfoam Gebru\", \"from\": 3987, \"to\": 4001}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4006, \"to\": 4018}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's good to have African riders in the Olympics, but I am even happier to see Ethiopian female riders at the Paris Olympic Games.\\\"\", \"from\": 4020, \"to\": 4151, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4099, \"end\": 4108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia\", \"score\": 0.9999999827005014, \"rank\": 1.7299628731874265e-08, \"text\": \"Ethiopian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"African riders\", \"from\": 4038, \"to\": 4052}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4056, \"to\": 4068}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympic Games\", \"from\": 4126, \"to\": 4149}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An increase in the total number of participants in the women's road race and the widening of qualification criteria has meant that more women can take part from a broader range of countries.\", \"from\": 4153, \"to\": 4343, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"An increase\", \"from\": 4153, \"to\": 4164}, {\"ngram\": \"the total number\", \"from\": 4168, \"to\": 4184}, {\"ngram\": \"participants\", \"from\": 4188, \"to\": 4200}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's road race\", \"from\": 4204, \"to\": 4225}, {\"ngram\": \"the widening\", \"from\": 4230, \"to\": 4242}, {\"ngram\": \"qualification c