 \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lovina_Beach\"}, {\"begin\": 4651, \"end\": 4662, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canyon\\u2013SRAM\", \"score\": 0.9999999999499778, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Canyon-SRAM\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canyon\\u2013SRAM\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canyon\\u2013SRAM\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that trend\", \"from\": 4692, \"to\": 4702}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 4718, \"to\": 4725}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 4772, \"to\": 4776}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic road race\", \"from\": 4780, \"to\": 4801}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After winning the African Continental Championships in Ghana and the Nigerian National Championships in 2023, the 25-year-old was told the good news.\", \"from\": 4804, \"to\": 4953, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4859, \"end\": 4864, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ghana\", \"score\": 0.9983663699459497, \"rank\": 0.001636303167682059, \"text\": \"Ghana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ghana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ghana\"}, {\"begin\": 4873, \"end\": 4881, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9946138146185827, \"rank\": 0.00274530693298347, \"text\": \"Nigerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}, {\"begin\": 4882, \"end\": 4904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics_National_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 4.3923306078659234e-13, \"text\": \"National Championships\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics_National_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics_National_Championships\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the African Continental Championships\", \"from\": 4818, \"to\": 4855}, {\"ngram\": \"the good news\", \"from\": 4939, \"to\": 4952}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I never expected to go to the Olympics, but I just tried my best.\", \"from\": 4955, \"to\": 5021, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4982, \"to\": 4994}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When they told me I'd qualified for the Olympics, I was so happy,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 5022, \"to\": 5098, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 5058, \"to\": 5070}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have been to Paris before for the World Track Championships but I have not ridden on the course for the road race.\", \"from\": 5100, \"to\": 5217, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5116, \"end\": 5121, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 1.1629439619046698e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the World Track Championships\", \"from\": 5133, \"to\": 5162}, {\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 5188, \"to\": 5198}, {\"ngram\": \"the road race\", \"from\": 5203, \"to\": 5216}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have just seen it on my phone.\", \"from\": 5218, \"to\": 5250, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my phone\", \"from\": 5241, \"to\": 5249}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My first international competition was at the Road Race World Championships in Glasgow last year.\", \"from\": 5252, \"to\": 5350, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5332, \"end\": 5339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"score\": 0.9999985416763313, \"rank\": 1.4583254592296522e-06, \"text\": \"Glasgow\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My first international competition\", \"from\": 5253, \"to\": 5287}, {\"ngram\": \"the Road Race World Championships\", \"from\": 5295, \"to\": 5328}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was so scary.\", \"from\": 5351, \"to\": 5369, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I could not believe I was there and was so overwhelmed.\", \"from\": 5370, \"to\": 5425, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was thinking, 'Wow, is this for real?'\", \"from\": 5426, \"to\": 5466, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not scared anymore.\", \"from\": 5467, \"to\": 5491, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To be frank, in Paris, I just want to finish the race.\", \"from\": 5492, \"to\": 5546, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5508, \"end\": 5513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 1.1629439619046698e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 5537, \"to\": 5545}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nobody who goes to a race does not want to win, but I know cycling is not an easy sport, so I will try my best to be in a good position and stay with the group.\\\"\", \"from\": 5547, \"to\": 5708, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nobody\", \"from\": 5547, \"to\": 5553}, {\"ngram\": \"a race\", \"from\": 5566, \"to\": 5572}, {\"ngram\": \"cycling\", \"from\": 5606, \"to\": 5613}, {\"ngram\": \"an easy sport\", \"from\": 5621, \"to\": 5634}, {\"ngram\": \"a good position\", \"from\": 5667, \"to\": 5682}, {\"ngram\": \"the group\", \"from\": 5697, \"to\": 5706}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the Girona-based rider, who also juggles racing with jointly managing a hair and beauty business with her sister in Abuja, things are a far cry from growing up on a farm in the Delta region of the country of Nigeria.\", \"from\": 5710, \"to\": 5930, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5830, \"end\": 5835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abuja\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9636142229374175e-29, \"text\": \"Abuja\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abuja\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abuja\"}, {\"begin\": 5922, \"end\": 5929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9976572097341563, \"rank\": 0.0023482918210202147, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Girona-based rider\", \"from\": 5714, \"to\": 5736}, {\"ngram\": \"a hair and beauty business\", \"from\": 5784, \"to\": 5810}, {\"ngram\": \"her sister\", \"from\": 5816, \"to\": 5826}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 5837, \"to\": 5843}, {\"ngram\": \"a far cry\", \"from\": 5848, \"to\": 5857}, {\"ngram\": \"a farm\", \"from\": 5877, \"to\": 5883}, {\"ngram\": \"the Delta region\", \"from\": 5887, \"to\": 5903}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 5907, \"to\": 5918}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We would use bikes to go to the farm and to fetch water.\", \"from\": 5932, \"to\": 5989, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bikes\", \"from\": 5946, \"to\": 5951}, {\"ngram\": \"the farm\", \"from\": 5961, \"to\": 5969}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 5983, \"to\": 5988}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then somebody from my village saw me and said, 'You could be a cyclist', and I said, 'What is cycling?'.\", \"from\": 5990, \"to\": 6094, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"somebody\", \"from\": 5995, \"to\": 6003}, {\"ngram\": \"my village\", \"from\": 6009, \"to\": 6019}, {\"ngram\": \"a cyclist\", \"from\": 6051, \"to\": 6060}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was at school thanks to a running scholarship.\", \"from\": 6095, \"to\": 6143, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"school\", \"from\": 6104, \"to\": 6110}, {\"ngram\": \"thanks\", \"from\": 6111, \"to\": 6117}, {\"ngram\": \"a running scholarship\", \"from\": 6121, \"to\": 6142}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not know anything about cycle racing, but I decided to have a go at it.\", \"from\": 6144, \"to\": 6221, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 6159, \"to\": 6167}, {\"ngram\": \"cycle racing\", \"from\": 6174, \"to\": 6186}, {\"ngram\": \"a go\", \"from\": 6210, \"to\": 6214}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the start, it was somewhat stressful for me because the road bike was very different from my home bike and very uncomfortable.\", \"from\": 6222, \"to\": 6351, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 6225, \"to\": 6234}, {\"ngram\": \"the road bike\", \"from\": 6277, \"to\": 6290}, {\"ngram\": \"my home bike\", \"from\": 6315, \"to\": 6327}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But after one month, and with encouragement from my mum, before I lost her, I was able to do it.\\\"\", \"from\": 6352, \"to\": 6449, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one month\", \"from\": 6362, \"to\": 6371}, {\"ngram\": \"encouragement\", \"from\": 6382, \"to\": 6395}, {\"ngram\": \"my mum\", \"from\": 6401, \"to\": 6407}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ese worked hard in her training and rode with different groups.\", \"from\": 6451, \"to\": 6514, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ese\", \"from\": 6451, \"to\": 6454}, {\"ngram\": \"her training\", \"from\": 6470, \"to\": 6482}, {\"ngram\": \"different groups\", \"from\": 6497, \"to\": 6513}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The head of the Nigerian Cycling Federation, Giandomenico Massari, helped her develop her career, despite there being no sponsorship by the Federation.\", \"from\": 6515, \"to\": 6666, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6531, \"end\": 6539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9946138146185827, \"rank\": 0.00274530693298347, \"text\": \"Nigerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}, {\"begin\": 6540, \"end\": 6547, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Road_bicycle_racing\", \"score\": 0.9999999978444976, \"rank\": 1.319846818674497e-09, \"text\": \"Cycling\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Road_bicycle_racing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Road_bicycle_racing\"}, {\"begin\": 6560, \"end\": 6572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giovanni_Domenico_Tiepolo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Giandomenico\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giovanni_Domenico_Tiepolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giovanni_Domenico_Tiepolo\"}, {\"begin\": 6573, \"end\": 6580, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Massari\", \"score\": 0.9999999672809287, \"rank\": 3.2719228845878914e-08, \"text\": \"Massari\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Massari\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Massari\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The head\", \"from\": 6515, \"to\": 6523}, {\"ngram\": \"her career\", \"from\": 6601, \"to\": 6611}, {\"ngram\": \"no sponsorship\", \"from\": 6633, \"to\": 6647}, {\"ngram\": \"the Federation\", \"from\": 6651, \"to\": 6665}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Based on her victories in continental and national championships, she eventually secured a place in the Canyon-SRAM Generation team in early 2024.\", \"from\": 6667, \"to\": 6813, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her victories\", \"from\": 6676, \"to\": 6689}, {\"ngram\": \"continental and national championships\", \"from\": 6693, \"to\": 6731}, {\"ngram\": \"a place\", \"from\": 6756, \"to\": 6763}, {\"ngram\": \"the Canyon-SRAM Generation team\", \"from\": 6767, \"to\": 6798}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although Ese receives a lot of encouragement from her sisters, in general, women's cycling in Nigeria is not encouraged.\", \"from\": 6815, \"to\": 6935, \"entities\": [{\"